-- Italy Scooter, Motorcycle Sales May Drop 20% in 2010, Industry Group Says
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-08-02T13:03:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/italy-scooter-motorcycle-sales-may-drop-20-in-2010-industry-group-says.html

          
          
             Sales of motorcycles and scooters may
drop 20 percent to 400,000 units this year in Italy, industry
association Ancma said by e-mail today.  
 That corresponds to a sales slump of 400 million euros, the
statement said.  
          
          


  


        